<h3 data-section-id="vw6dtn" data-start="993" data-end="1014">Push it to GitHub</h3>
<p data-start="1015" data-end="1027">In Git Bash:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1029" data-end="1240"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fxfgsfqf.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fxfgsfqf.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> init</span><br><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> add .</span><br><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> commit </span><span class="ͼn">-m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼk">"Initial creator portfolio website"</span><br><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> branch </span><span class="ͼn">-M</span><span> main</span><br><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/social-link-portfolio.git</span><br><span class="ͼl">git</span><span> push </span><span class="ͼn">-u</span><span> origin main</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="1yt4ggm" data-start="1242" data-end="1273">Turn it into a live website</h3>
<p data-start="1274" data-end="1284">On GitHub:</p>
<ol data-start="1285" data-end="1455">
<li data-section-id="1bxdxhb" data-start="1285" data-end="1301">
<p data-start="1288" data-end="1301">Open the repo</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="amc1in" data-start="1302" data-end="1323">
<p data-start="1305" data-end="1323">Go to <strong data-start="1311" data-end="1323">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11g85na" data-start="1324" data-end="1342">
<p data-start="1327" data-end="1342">Click <strong data-start="1333" data-end="1342">Pages</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2anpmb" data-start="1343" data-end="1395">
<p data-start="1346" data-end="1395">Under <strong data-start="1352" data-end="1362">Source</strong>, choose <strong data-start="1371" data-end="1395">Deploy from a branch</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tx5764" data-start="1396" data-end="1447">
<p data-start="1399" data-end="1406">Select:</p>
<ul data-start="1410" data-end="1447">
<li data-section-id="15hmgtp" data-start="1410" data-end="1426">
<p data-start="1412" data-end="1426">Branch: <code data-start="1420" data-end="1426">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cgd099" data-start="1430" data-end="1447">
<p data-start="1432" data-end="1447">Folder: <code data-start="1440" data-end="1447">/root</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ruuggs" data-start="1448" data-end="1455">
<p data-start="1451" data-end="1455">Save</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1457" data-end="1495">Your live link will be something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1497" data-end="1570"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fxfgsfqf.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-fxfgsfqf.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-h