markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="136">You want something that feels like a <strong data-start="37" data-end="46">brand</strong>, not just a username — especially since you’re building <em data-start="103" data-end="118">TheAdamEffect</em> as your identity.</p>
<p data-start="138" data-end="192">Here are the <strong data-start="151" data-end="191">best directions for YOU specifically</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="194" data-end="197">
<h1 data-section-id="1mlyqcb" data-start="199" data-end="244">🔥 Top Tier (Brand-Level – Use These First)</h1>
<ul data-start="246" data-end="396">
<li data-section-id="sp8hqw" data-start="246" data-end="296">
<p data-start="248" data-end="296"><strong data-start="248" data-end="265">TheAdamEffect</strong> ⭐ (BEST — matches your TikTok)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1h3xyra" data-start="297" data-end="313">
<p data-start="299" data-end="313"><strong data-start="299" data-end="313">AdamEffect</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="h6vsmn" data-start="314" data-end="332">
<p data-start="316" data-end="332"><strong data-start="316" data-end="332">AdamEffectHQ</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y06zo9" data-start="333" data-end="352">
<p data-start="335" data-end="352"><strong data-start="335" data-end="352">AdamEffectLab</strong></p>
